body_html: I think this is a dependency issue. The latest version(1.13.1) of numpy is used during compilation. However, if you use xgboost, the numpy version should be downgraded to 1.12.1. In order to solve this issue, you should compile either xgboost or pytorch on your own using the same numpy version.
